      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i think something is actually wrong with the way i'm seeing things lately. like, i was driving to work today and i passed this specific patch of sidewalk near the park, and i swear the texture of the concrete just... looped. like it was the exact same crack and the exact same discoloration repeated every few feet in a perfect line. it didnt look like a trick of the light, it looked like a literal copy-paste error. has anyone else ever noticed stuff like that?",
